messages.title: It's a two-horse race in Camden
messages.content: Only the Lib Dems can beat Labour here. Ladbrokes predict Conservatives will finish 3rd again in this constituency.

messages.title: It's Lib Dems or Labour here
messages.content: Here in Camden, only Jo Shaw and the Liberal Democrats can beat Labour. The Conservatives are set to come a distant 3rd.

messages.title: A fresh start With Jo Shaw and the Lib Dems
messages.content: Jo Shaw and the local Lib Dem team are fighting and delivering for you.

messages.title: More of the same with another Labour MP
messages.content: Labour have let us all down. They've neglected Camden. Failed local people.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Jo Shaw is energetic and passionate campaigner. She lives in Camden and is fighting alongside local people to get things done.
Jo Shaw fought alongside local residents to save our local police stations and is campaigning against Labour's health cuts.
